ovica]], [[Bogatić]] ||align=right| 67.01 |- |[[Lake Ludaš]]||1982 ||[[Subotica]]||align=right|8.46 |- |[[Pastures of the Great Bustard]] || || [[Čoka]], [[Kikinda]] ||align=right| 9.79 |- |[[Suva Planina]] || proposed<ref name=registar/> || [[Bela Palanka]], [[Gadžin Han]], [[Niš]] ||align=right| 181.76 |- |[[Jerma]] || proposed<ref name=registar/> || [[Babušnica]], [[Dimitrovgrad, Serbia|Dimitrovgrad]], [[Pirot]] ||align=right| 65.63 |- |[[Titelski Breg]] || proposed<ref name=registar/> || [[Titel]] ||align=right| 3.33 |- |[[Goč]] || proposed<ref name=registar/> || [[Kraljevo]] ||align=right| |- |[[Brzansko Moravište]] || proposed<ref name=registar/> || [[Jagodina]], [[Batočina]] ||align=right| 0.65 |- |[[Okanj]] || proposed<ref name=registar/> || [[Zrenjanin]], [[Novi Bečej]] ||align=right| 56.78 |- |}
