==Natural monuments== There are currently 64 natural monuments of geological heritage and 225 monuments of botanical heritage (mostly rare trees)<ref name=registar/> in Serbia. Some of the best known monuments of geological heritage are: [[Resavska cave]], [[Đavolja Varoš]], [[Marble Cave, Kosovo|Marble cave]] and [[Rugova Canyon]].
